NWQ Investment Management Co., LLC


                  NWQ Investment Management (NWQ) is a value manager that offers a variety of investment strategies including: large-cap value, special equity, concentrated equity, small/mid-cap value, small-cap value, balanced, core fixed-income and alternative investments. The firm's investment approach is based on bottom-up, fundamental research that seeks to identify potential investments that are trading at attractive absolute valuations. They strive to capitalize on disparities between investor perceptions and underlying fundamentals in the capital markets. NWQ's approach is finance-oriented and cash flow-focused. Their strategies focus on attractive valuations, downside protection and the identification of catalysts and inflection points.                




